---
// Module 3: Embodied AI — stepping into reality
---

<section class="section embodied-section" id="embodied-ai">
  <!-- Scan decoration -->
  <div class="scan-line" aria-hidden="true" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="embodied-header">
      <div class="section-tag animate-on-scroll">Embodied AI</div>
      <h2 class="section-title animate-on-scroll">Intelligence Beyond the Screen</h2>
      <p class="section-desc animate-on-scroll">
        AI is no longer confined to displays and data centers. Embodied intelligence perceives, reasons, and acts within the physical world — assisting humans in complex tasks and freeing people from dangerous and grueling labor.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Two-column cards -->
    <div class="embodied-grid">
      <div class="glass-card ar-card embodied-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="embodied-icon">🏭</div>
        <h3>Industrial Partnership</h3>
        <p>In manufacturing floors and warehouses, embodied robots work alongside humans — handling heavy loads, precision assembly, and hazardous operations with tireless accuracy.</p>
        <div class="card-data mono-label">SECTOR: INDUSTRY 4.0</div>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-card ar-card embodied-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="embodied-icon">🏠</div>
        <h3>Daily Life Assistance</h3>
        <p>From household chores to elderly care, embodied AI extends a helping hand into the most intimate spaces — enhancing independence and quality of life for everyone.</p>
        <div class="card-data mono-label">SECTOR: DOMESTIC</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Central highlight -->
    <div class="embodied-highlight animate-on-scroll">
      <blockquote>
        <p>"The true power of AI is realized when it can touch, move, and transform the physical world — not just process its data."</p>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .embodied-section {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-deep) 0%, var(--bg-secondary) 50%, var(--bg-deep) 100%);
  }

  .embodied-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 660px;
    margin: 0 auto 3.5rem;
  }

  .embodied-header .section-tag { justify-content: center; }
  .embodied-header .section-tag::before { display: none; }

  .embodied-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .embodied-card { padding: 2rem; }

  .embodied-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .embodied-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .embodied-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .card-data {
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    padding-top: 0.75rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .embodied-highlight {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    background: var(--glass);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    position: relative;
  }

  .embodied-highlight::before {
    content: '"';
    position: absolute;
    top: -0.5rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    font-size: 5rem;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    color: var(--magenta);
    opacity: 0.12;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .embodied-highlight p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .embodied-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
